4
00:00:13.949 --> 00:00:23.439
{"en":"The big clock which used to strike the hours day and night was damaged many years ago and has been silent ever since. ^ ","ch":"教堂的钟很大， 以前不分昼夜打点报时， 但在很多年前遭到毁坏， 从此便无声无息了。  "}

5
