6
00:00:30.746 --> 00:00:38.825
{"en":"Looking at his watch,  he saw that it was one o'clock,  but the bell struck thirteen times before it stopped. ^ ","ch":"他一看表， 才1点钟， 可是那钟一边敲了13下才停。  "}

7
00:00:38.975 --> 00:00:44.990
{"en":"Armed with a torch,  the vicar went up into the clock tower to see what was going on. ^ ","ch":"牧师拿着一支电筒走上钟楼想去看看究竟发生了什么事情。  "}

8
00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:53.192
{"en":"In the torchlight,  he caught sight of a figure whom he immediately recognized as Bill Wilkins,  our local grocer. ^ ","ch":"借着电筒光。 他看见一个人， 马上认出那是本地杂货店店主比尔. 威尔金斯。  "}

9
00:00:53.342 --> 00:00:58.155
{"en":"'Whatever are you doing up here Bill? ' asked the vicar in surprise. ^ ","ch":"你究竟在这上面干什么， 比尔? ”牧师惊讶地问。  "}

10
00:00:58.305 --> 00:01:01.786
{"en":"'I'm trying to repair the bell, ' answered Bill. ^ ","ch":"我想把这口钟修好， ”比尔回答说。  "}

11
00:01:01.936 --> 00:01:05.339
{"en":"'I've been coming up here night after night for weeks now. ^ ","ch":"好几个星期了， 我天天夜里到钟楼上来。  "}

12
00:01:05.489 --> 00:01:08.683
{"en":"You see,  I was hoping to give you a surprise. '^ ","ch":"嗯， 我是想让你大吃一惊。 ” "}

13
00:01:08.833 --> 00:01:12.314
{"en":"'You certainly did give me a surprise! ' said the vicar. ^ ","ch":"你确实使我大吃了一惊！ ”牧师说，  "}

14
00:01:12.464 --> 00:01:15.997
{"en":"'You've probably woken up everyone in the village as well. ^ ","ch":"也许同时你把村里所有的人都吵醒了。  "}

15
00:01:16.147 --> 00:01:19.079
{"en":"Still,  I'm glad the bell is working again. '^ ","ch":"不过， 钟又能报时了， 我还是很高兴的。 ” "}

16
