{"en":"'That's the trouble,  vicar, ' answered Bill. ^ “","ch":"问题就在这里， 牧师， ”比尔回答说。  "}

17
00:01:22.051 --> 00:01:30.913
{"en":"'It's working all right,  but I'm afraid that at one o'clock it will strike thirteen times and there's nothing I can do about it. '^ ","ch":"不错， 钟能报时了， 但是， 恐怕每到1点钟， 它总要敲13下， 对此我已无能为力了。 ” "}

18
